title: Shreeman Aashique
subTitle: Vishwamitra, a professor who dissuades marriages, and his follower, Dushant, fall in love with Shakuntala. However, when Vishwamitra learns about this, he decides to separate the two.

title: Professor Ki Padosan
subTitle: Vidyadhar, a Hindi professor, leads a blissful life with his wife and son. However, their peace is disrupted when Menaka walks into Vidyadhar's life and tries to seduce him for revenge.

title: Plan
subTitle: Four friends Bobby, Lucky, Jai and Omi arrive in Mumbai with dreams of making it big. They kidnap a businessman hoping to extort money from him, but he turns out to be a gangster.

title: Aulad
subTitle: Believing his wife to be dead, Anand gives up his own child to Yashoda, who has lost her husband and her baby. However, he faces a dilemma when his wife returns.

title: Jeevan Ek Sanghursh
subTitle: Karan, a good-hearted thief, is compelled to work for a criminal mastermind. However, things take a turn when he reunites with his estranged family and tries to leave the underworld.

title: Saajan Chale Sasural
subTitle: After Shyamsunder presumes that his first wife Pooja died in a flood, he marries Divya. When he learns that Pooja is alive, he has to juggle between his wives, keeping both his marriages a secret.

title: Aurat Teri Yehi Kahani
subTitle: Savitri, a motherless girl, is forced to marry an elderly man for her family's sake. However, after her husband's sudden death, her life takes a turn for the worse.

title: Pyar Ke Naam Qurbaan
subTitle: Billu attempts to play Holi with Devika, but she gets him arrested. In an attempt to take revenge, he kidnaps her, which infuriates her brother, who sets out to save her.

title: Jawani Zindabad
subTitle: Shashi gets his sister married to Ravi without offering dowry in order to take a stand against the practice. However, he gets harassed by his sister's in-laws for his stance.

title: Maharaja
subTitle: Prince Kohinoor returns home after twenty years only to discover that Ranbir Singh, his parents' killer, still holds control. Subsequently, he decides to defeat him to protect his loved ones.

title: Maharaja
subTitle: Prince Kohinoor returns home after twenty years only to discover that Ranbir Singh, his parents' killer, still holds control. Subsequently, he decides to defeat him to protect his loved ones.

title: Zabardast
subTitle: While being on the run from Balram, a gangster, Ratan's family gets tragically separated. However, after serving in prison, Ratan emerges to seek revenge on Balram, who uses Ratan's son against him.

title: Comedy Station
subTitle: Various talented comedians perform hilarious skits and stand-up acts on diverse themes and topics to entertain the audience.

title: Doli Saja Ke Rakhna
subTitle: Inder and Pallavi fall for each other but her three possessive brothers hate him. Resultantly, the couple elopes but they soon find themselves missing their families and decide to return.

title: Sadak
subTitle: A young man who falls in love with a sex worker must overcome the social stigma as well as face the brothel owner and some criminal elements.

title: Paap Ki Duniya
subTitle: Suraj, a criminal, and Vijay, a policeman, vie for each other's blood, unaware that they are brothers. Things turn more complicated when they both fall in love with the same woman.

title: Eeshwar
subTitle: Eeswar is a motherless child who hates his father for remarrying after his mother's death. He falls for a local politician's daughter which lands him in trouble.

title: Naajayaz
subTitle: Jai and Sandhya pursue gangster Raj Solanki, but the case takes a shocking twist when Jai discovers Raj is his long-lost father.

title: Shola Aur Shabnam
subTitle: Divya loves Karan and plans to get married to him. However, a notorious gangster's brother, Bali, who also has his eyes on her, goes to great lengths to destroy her relationship with Karan.

title: Maidan-E-Jung
subTitle: Data Guru, a powerful man, spreads terror in his village. Later, when a villager marries his widowed daughter-in-law, he sets out to seek revenge.

title: Maidan-E-Jung
subTitle: Data Guru, a powerful man, spreads terror in his village. Later, when a villager marries his widowed daughter-in-law, he sets out to seek revenge.

title: Sangharsh
subTitle: Reet, a police officer, learns about a religious fanatic, Pandey, who abducts children. She then joins forces with a prisoner in order to punish Pandey.

title: Mere Jeevan Saathi
subTitle: Prakash, an altruistic artist turned womaniser, falls in love with Jyoti. However, situation changes when he loses his eyesight after an accident and Kamini, a socialite, tortures him.

title: Insidious: Chapter 3
subTitle: Quinn, a young girl, reaches out to a powerful psychic to help her contact her recently deceased mother. However, her plan backfires when an evil spirit makes Quinn a host and hurts her physically.

title: Mastana
subTitle: Satya, a poor man, befriends a rich but neglected child, but her parents resent their friendship and force him to leave. However, when she falls gravely ill, they ask Satya to return.

title: Bhai Ho To Aisa
subTitle: When all the family property is left to Bharat, his brother wants to kill him for the wealth. Bharat overhears his plan and plays along only to return as a dacoit to set things right.

title: Haath Ki Safai
subTitle: Brothers Raju and Shankar, who are separated by fate, cross paths with each other in Mumbai when Kamini, a wealthy runaway, unintentionally barges into their lives.

title: Aradhana
subTitle: After Arun dies in a plane crash, Vandana gives up her child for adoption as she and Arun married in secret. But, she works as a nanny for the family that adopted her son to stay close to him.

title: Ramkali
subTitle: Inspector Sultan becomes a fugitive and bandit, driven by a quest for vengeance. Later, he crosses paths with a dancer, Ramkali, and discovers that she is also seeking retribution.

title: Aa Gale Lag Jaa
subTitle: Prem, a young man, must part from his lover Preeti even though she is pregnant. Years later, they reunite, but Preeti is about to engage another man.

title: Chacha Bhatija
subTitle: Teja, a widower, marries Sonia, a girl who only wants to get her hands on his inheritance. So, she creates animosity between Teja, his brother and his son.
